context: for the charity! a very admirable target.gill aims to raise funds through her own sponsorships, and hopefully via any willing customers of her fish and chip shops. grids will be displayed in the shops, numbered 1 to 100 and customers will be able to buy a square for a minimum donation of £1. for every 100 squares sold, gill will provide one lucky winner with a free fish and chip meal for up to a family of four!if you’re passing one of her fish and chip shops in wibsey, allerton or ilkley then please pop in, grab some fantastic fish and chips and help marie curie by buying a square!
